oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Risk of an Altered Interestrus Interval Following Clinical Mastitis in Dairy Cattle
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Moore, D. A.
Cullor, J.
Bondurant, R. H.
Sischo, W. M.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: clinical mastitis
reproductive records
interestrus
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Clinical mastitis and reproductive records from two southern California dairy herds were used in a cross-sectional study to determine the risk of an altered interestrus interval following clinical mastitis.
